mirror your life in any way?

29:56.861 --> 29:58.294
Or...

29:59.230 --> 30:01.061
...are we really alone?

30:27.492 --> 30:29.187
What happened?

30:37.168 --> 30:38.829
What do you see?

31:03.795 --> 31:08.357
