32:32.951 --> 32:39.083
I went to the bathroom,
shut the door and picked up a razor.

32:42.694 --> 32:44.025
That was my first cut.

32:45.596 --> 32:49.225
But the last one
was seven years ago.

32:52.804 --> 32:54.863
You don't need to hide from me.

33:28.606 --> 33:30.870
- I better go.
- No, stay.

33:31.042 --> 33:32.669
