33:58.803 --> 34:00.737
Young. Of course.

34:00.905 --> 34:03.169
- Strong.
- Strong. Great, yep.

34:03.341 --> 34:06.310
They wanna be respected.
I mean, I wanna be respected.

34:06.477 --> 34:09.071
And successful.
They wanna be successful.

34:09.246 --> 34:10.373
- Jules.
- Yes?

34:10.547 --> 34:11.572
