37:49.533 --> 37:51.535
Well, where are you?

38:02.647 --> 38:04.478
Park your car.

38:04.649 --> 38:05.775
What are you doing?

38:06.350 --> 38:08.545
You got to take pictures of me.

38:08.719 --> 38:12.211
